desc_short	-----								Dark Storm: VR Missions is a single-player stealth/action game in which you take control of Amber Kingsley, a new security recruit at the Irving Apex Research Facility. Before beginning her work, Amber must first undergo VR training where her skills will be pushed to the limit.							
developer									Fenrir Studios								
